docs.lead_paragraph: Ireland is debating its ban on abortion again as doctors keep a brain-dead pregnant woman on life support, awaiting a judge's verdict on what do to with the living fetus.

headline.main: Irish Face New Abortion Row Over Brain-Dead Woman
